name: Experiment Or Die #147
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. You never really know where and when different opportunities will come from. All you can do is put yourself out there, try and position yourself to be present and be OPEN to new experiences, new people and new encounters. More or less, if there is a staircase in front of you, walk up the stairs! Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
